What is Impersonal.me?

Impersonal.me is an online SEO tool designed to deliver impersonal search results from Google. When you search on Google, the results are often influenced by your personal search history and geographical location, which can create personalisation in the search results displayed. Impersonal.me eliminates these factors by presenting search results that are not tailored to the individual user.

This tool is particularly useful for SEO specialists and digital marketers who want to see how their company's website ranks in search results without the influence of personalisation. By using Impersonal.me, you can get a more objective picture of how an average user will experience the search results.

In addition, Impersonal.me allows you to simulate searches from different geographical locations. This means you can see what search results look like for users in other countries, which is valuable if you work with international SEO or want to understand how your company (or its competitors) is performing across different markets.

 

How do you use Impersonal.me?

To use Impersonal.me, simply enter your keyword in the search field and select the desired settings under 'Options' (such as language and country). Then click 'GO', after which you will be redirected to Google and presented with impersonal search results based on your specifications.
